  <title>Manage automatic playlists</title>
  
  <p>
    To create an automatic playlist:
  </p>
  
  <steps>
    <item>
      <p>
        Choose <guiseq><gui style="menu">Music</gui><gui style="menuitem">Playlists</gui><gui style="menuitem">New Automatic Playlist</gui></guiseq>.
      </p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p> 
        Make your choices, and when done click <gui style="button">New</gui>.
      </p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>
        The new playlist will be added 
      </p>
    </item>
  </steps>

